---------------------------------
         Design a Bird
---------------------------------
Requirements :

1.Create following types of Bird
    1. Pigeon
    2. Crow
    3. Sparrow
    4. Ostrich
    5. Penguin
2. Penguin & Ostrich don't fly.
3. Crow & Pigeon fly in same way & sparrow flies in different way
4. Every bird can Eat, Sing.





